1. Information we may collect

Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 collects information in order to provide better services to all users. The main sources of information collected by Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 are: information you provide to Traffic Tycoon Empire, information obtained by Traffic Tycoon Empire during your use of Traffic Tycoon Empire products and services, and your information shared by third parties. The types of information collected by Traffic Tycoon Empire mainly include the following:

1. Personal information

Personal information refers to various information that can be individually or combined with other information to identify the personal identity of a natural person, including but not limited to the natural personâ€™s name, date of birth, ID number, personal biometric information, address, Phone number etc.

When you register an account or use Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 products and services, with your consent and confirmation, Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 may collect the relevant personal information you provide, such as name, gender, age, date of birth, ID number, bank card number , Email address, phone number, mailing address, occupation, education level, etc.

2. Equipment information

Equipment information refers to the information of the equipment used when you use Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 products or services.

When you use Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 products or services, Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 will collect information about the devices you use Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 products or services, such as device name, device model, device identification code, operating system and application version, language settings, Resolution, service provider network ID (pLMN), etc. This information can help Traffic Tycoon Empire provide you with better information display or product services.

3. Location information

Location information refers to the information about your location collected when you turn on the device positioning function and use the related services provided by Traffic Tycoon Empire based on location, including:

(1) When you turn on the device positioning function and use Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 related products or services, Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 may use GpS, WiFi or other technical methods to collect and process information about your actual location.

(2) Real-time information including your geographic location provided by you or other users. For example, shared information uploaded by you or others showing your current or previous geographic location, and geotag information contained in photos shared by you or others.

(3) If you do not want to be accessed, you can choose to turn off the relevant functions of the device or product/service, but this may affect Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 to provide you with relevant services.

4. Log information

Refers to when you use Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 products and services, the system may automatically collect certain information through cookies or other methods and store it in server logs. Such information may include:

(1) Detailed usage of Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 products and services, such as the web search terms you use, the page address you visit, and other information and content details that you browse or request when using Traffic Tycoon Empire services; user habits Statistical data, such as setting item information when using the Traffic Tycoon Empire input method, the number of uses of some buttons, the number of words on the screen, etc. This type of data is anonymous, and Traffic Tycoon Empire cannot locate specific users based on the uploaded data .

(2) Device or software information, such as the configuration information provided by your mobile device, web browser or other programs used to access Traffic Tycoon Empire products or services, the version and device identification code used by the mobile device, etc.

(3) Equipment event information, such as crashes, system activities, etc.

(4) Ip address.

5. Other information collected after your consent.


