Fourth, our information security protection

1. Idle Traffic Tycoon will only retain your personal information for the period necessary for the purpose described in this policy and within the time limit required by laws and regulations.

2. Data security technical measures: Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 will adopt security protection measures that meet industry standards, including establishing reasonable system specifications and security technologies to prevent your personal information from unauthorized access, use, modification, and data damage Or lost; Traffic Tycoon Empire will use security technology and procedures to monitor and record network operation status and network security incidents, and take necessary technical measures to ensure network security to prevent information loss, improper use, unauthorized reading or disclosure. For example, in some services, Traffic Tycoon Empire will use encryption technology to protect the personal information you provide. However, please understand that due to technical limitations and various malicious methods that may exist, in the Internet industry, even if you do your best to strengthen security measures, it is impossible to always guarantee 100% security of information. You need to understand that the system and communication network you use to access Traffic Tycoon Empire's products and services may have problems due to factors outside the controllable range of Traffic Tycoon Empire.

3. Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 only allows employees and partners who need to know this information to access personal information, and has set up strict access control and monitoring mechanisms for this purpose. Traffic Tycoon Empire also requires all persons who may have access to your personal information to perform corresponding confidentiality obligations. If you fail to fulfill these obligations, you may be held accountable or be suspended from the partnership with Traffic Tycoon Empire.

4. Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 will take all reasonable and feasible measures to ensure that irrelevant personal information is not collected. Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 will only retain your personal information for the period required to achieve the purpose stated in the policy, unless it is necessary to extend the retention period or is permitted by law.

5. The content and information you provide, upload or publish when you use Idle Traffic Tycoon 2's products and services (such as photos and other information about your personal activities) may reveal your personal information. You need to carefully consider whether to disclose relevant personal information when using Traffic Tycoon Empire's products and services. In some cases, you can control the range of users who have the right to browse your shared information through the privacy settings of certain products and services of Traffic Tycoon Empire.

6. The Internet is not an absolutely secure environment, and the communication methods with other users such as e-mail, instant messaging, social software, etc. cannot be determined whether it is completely encrypted. Traffic Tycoon Empire recommends that you use complex passwords when using such tools, and take care to protect you Security of personal information.

7. Security incident handling: In order to deal with possible risks such as personal information leakage, damage and loss, Idle Traffic Tycoon 2 has established a special emergency response team, in accordance with the companyâ€™s relevant security incident handling specifications, and launches security plans for different security incidents. Stop loss, analyze, formulate remedial measures, and cooperate with relevant departments to trace the source and crack down. At the same time, Traffic Tycoon Empire will promptly inform you in accordance with the requirements of laws and regulations: the basic situation and possible impact of the security incident, the disposal measures that Traffic Tycoon Empire has taken or will take, and suggestions that you can prevent and reduce risks on your own. Remedial measures, etc. At the same time, Traffic Tycoon Empire will promptly notify you of the incident by e-mail, letter, telephone, push notification, etc. If it is difficult to inform the subject of personal information one by one, Traffic Tycoon Empire will take a reasonable and effective way to issue an announcement. At the same time, Traffic Tycoon Empire will also proactively report the handling of personal information security incidents in accordance with the requirements of the regulatory authorities.


